Package: SeqAlignment
Title: Global sequence alignment for nucleotide sequeces
Version: 0.0.99
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Francesco",
           family = "Morettini",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "francesco.morettini@mail.polimi.it")
Description: This R package has been developed in order to find the optimal
    global alignment between two nucleotide sequences, using both the
    Needleman-Wunsch (NW) and the FOGSAA algorithms.
